00:00:05,067 --> 00:00:06,400
woman:
With Google Friend Connect,

2
00:00:06,400 --> 00:00:09,901
you can now add a social bar
to your Web site.

3
00:00:09,901 --> 00:00:11,901
To add a social bar,

4
00:00:11,901 --> 00:00:15,734
go to google.com/friendconnect,

5
00:00:15,734 --> 00:00:17,667
click on your Web site,

6
00:00:17,667 --> 00:00:21,000
and select social bar.

7
00:00:22,901 --> 00:00:26,167
Then scroll down the page
to choose your options.

8
00:00:27,567 --> 00:00:30,834
Then click generate code.

9
00:00:32,400 --> 00:00:35,234
Copy the code...

10
00:00:35,234 --> 00:00:37,067
and paste it into the body

11
00:00:37,067 --> 00:00:39,634
of your Web site's HTML.

12
00:00:39,634 --> 00:00:41,000
Now...

13
00:00:41,000 --> 00:00:43,067
you have successfully added

14
00:00:43,067 --> 00:00:45,734
a social bar to your site.

15
00:00:45,734 --> 00:00:48,234
This social bar
offers a snapshot

16
00:00:48,234 --> 00:00:52,033
of the activity taking place
on your Web site.

17
00:00:52,033 --> 00:00:54,901
Go to google.com/friendconnect

18
00:00:54,901 --> 00:00:56,667
to get started.

